T*
() Tj
T*
(A reviewer should ask:) Tj
T*
(- Can the contributor explain the work?) Tj
T*
(- Is there evidence of learning?) Tj
T*
(- Is the design choice documented?) Tj
T*
(- Is AI assistance disclosed or reviewed?) Tj
T*
(- Does the weekly report show what changed?) Tj
T*
(- Can another fellow continue from this commit?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Pull Request Review) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The pull request template requires:) Tj
T*
(- Branch from master.) Tj
T*
(- Weekly report update.) Tj
T*
(- Human learning evidence.) Tj
T*
(- Research note if a paper shaped the work.) Tj
T*
(- Design outcome if the architecture, data model, flow, or interface changed.) Tj
T*
(- Verification evidence.) Tj
T*
(- AI-use review.) Tj
